skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: aaa restaurants
Developer Terms of Use
des: Interact with AAA TourBook data for restaurants to find information on restaurants in your area. The skill needs you to have entered a location for your device in your Alexa companion app and to allow the AAA Restaurants Skill access to your location. Alexa can use the AAA Restaurants skill to explain the AAA Diamond rating system. Make sure to pronounce AAA as Triple A.
